## 어떻게 작업해야 하나

<https://github.com/code-yeongyu/oh-my-openagent/blob/dev/docs/guide/orchestration.md>

> | Complexity            | Approach                  | When to Use                                                                              |
> | --------------------- | ------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
> | **Simple**            | Just prompt               | Simple tasks, quick fixes, single-file changes                                           |
> | **Complex + Lazy**    | Type `ulw` or `ultrawork` | Complex tasks where explaining context is tedious. Agent figures it out.                 |
> | **Complex + Precise** | `@plan` → `/start-work`   | Precise, multi-step work requiring true orchestration. Prometheus plans, Atlas executes. |
>
> **Decision Flow:**
>
> ```
> Is it a quick fix or simple task?
>   └─ YES → Just prompt normally
>   └─ NO  → Is explaining the full context tedious?
>               └─ YES → Type "ulw" and let the agent figure it out
>               └─ NO  → Do you need precise, verifiable execution?
>                          └─ YES → Use @plan for Prometheus planning, then /start-work
>                          └─ NO  → Just use "ulw"
> ```

## Agent 뜻

<https://github.com/code-yeongyu/oh-my-openagent/blob/dev/docs/reference/features.md>

### Core Agents

Sisyphus:
The default orchestrator. Plans, delegates, and executes complex tasks using specialized subagents with aggressive parallel execution.

Hephaestus:
The Legitimate Craftsman. Autonomous deep worker inspired by AmpCode's deep mode.

Oracle:
Architecture consultation: GPT-5.4 or Claude Opus

Librarian:
Multi-repo analysis, documentation lookup, OSS implementation examples.
Research agents: cheap fast models are fine

Explore:
Fast codebase exploration and contextual grep.
Research agents: cheap fast models are fine

Multimodal-looker:
Visual content specialist. Analyzes PDFs, images, diagrams to extract information.

### Planning Agents

Prometheus:
Strategic planner with interview mode.

Momus:
Plan reviewer

Metis:
Plan consultant

### Orchestration Agents

Atlas:
Todo-list orchestrator.

sisyphus-junior:
Category-spawned executor.

